correctness.rationale: Major factual and schema issues. Key problems: (1) Numerous schema violations with nulls where numbers/objects are required: processParameters.pressure.quantityValue.numericValue, plasmaPower (set to null instead of omitting), thicknessControl.growthPerCycle.numberofCycles.quantityValue.numericValue, dosingTime[*].precursor/coReactant.numericValue, purgeTime[*].precursor/coReactant.numericValue, materialProperties.uniformity.variation.numericValue, conformality.aspectRatio.numericValue, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values.quantityValue.numericValue, roughness.value.quantityValue.numericValue, filmDensity.value.quantityValue.numericValue; filmComposition.atomicRatio.value uses "Not Found" which does not match the required colon-separated ratio format. (2) Flow rates are incorrectly assigned: 25 sccm reported in the article is the Ar carrier gas flow, not the precursor flow per compound; coReactant and purge flows are not provided in the article, yet set to null (schema-invalid). (3) Device properties mismatch the selected process: materialDeposited and supercycleDesign correspond to IGZO, but device metrics (μ_FE=59 cm^2/V·s, Vth=-7.36 V, SS=0.18, ION/IOFF=92.6) are from IZO (Table S1), not IGZO (Table S2). (4) Units/magnitudes wrong: subthresholdSwing is given as 0.18 with unit MilliV (should be ~180 mV if 0.18 V/dec); onOffRatio 92.6 is taken from a “×10^6” table header and should be 9.26e7 (dimensionless). (5) Crystallinity set to “amorphous” without explicit support in the provided text; XRD is mentioned but no phase result is reported here. (6) SupercycleDesign partially correct in order (In2O3→ZnO→Ga2O3) and counts (3:1:1) but lacks the explicit repetition (k) detail; acceptable but could be clearer. (7) Correct items include: TALD method, precursors (DADI/DEZ/TMGa) with ozone co-reactant, reactor (IC-100, MOMAN), substrate, temperature (210 °C), and GPC values from Supporting Fig. S1. To correct: align deviceProperties with a specific IGZO sample (e.g., 3IZGO: μ_FE=39.8 cm^2/V·s, Vth=-3.85 V, SS≈130 mV, ION/IOFF≈3.46e7), fix SS units, correct on/off magnitude, remove/omit optional fields rather than nulls, do not misuse carrier-gas flow as precursor flow, and only include values that are explicitly reported (or leave fields out if schema allows; otherwise this extraction cannot be schema-complete from the given article).

completeness.rationale: Extraction is largely incomplete and partially inconsistent with the article and the schema. Key issues: (1) Multiple distinct ALD processes in the paper are not represented: IZO series (2IZO, 3IZO, 4IZO, 5IZO), IGZO series with varying Ga (1IZGO, 2IZGO, 3IZGO), and bilayer-period variants (IZGO_S vs IZGO_L). Only one process instance is provided, so the supercycle designs, cycle counts, and device results per sample are missing. (2) Schema violations and nulls in required numeric fields: processParameters.pressure.numericValue, thicknessControl.numberofCycles.numericValue, nucleationPeriod.numericValue, dosingTime and purgeTime numeric values, flowRates.coReactantFlow and purgingGasFlow numeric values, materialProperties.uniformity.variation, conformality.aspectRatio, filmComposition.elementalConcentration.values, roughness.value, and filmDensity.value are all null but required to be numbers. atomicRatio.value is set to 'Not Found' instead of a valid ratio string. plasmaPower is present but set to null (should be omitted if not used). (3) Inconsistencies/mis-mapped values: deviceProperties populated with IZO data (μFE=59 cm²/V·s, Vth=-7.36 V, SS=0.18 V/dec, Ion/Ioff=92.6×10^6 per Table S1) while materialDeposited and supercycle include Ga (IGZO). SS unit is encoded as MilliV with value 0.18 (1000× too small); Ion/Ioff recorded as 92.6 unitless instead of 9.26e7; flowRates misuse 25 sccm as precursorFlow though 25 sccm refers to Ar carrier gas. (4) Supercycle design is underspecified: no repetition count k and no separate designs for the different samples; IZGO_S vs IZGO_L bilayer-period differences are not encoded. (5) Missing traceable film composition data: XPS composition trends and O 1s sub-peak area ratios reported in the text/figures are not captured; elemental concentrations and atomic ratios per sample are absent. To improve completeness, add separate process entries for each sample (2–5IZO; 1–3IZGO; IZGO_S/IZGO_L), correct units and magnitudes (SS in mV/dec, Ion/Ioff scale), map 25 sccm to carrier/purging flows, omit plasmaPower if thermal ALD, and populate (or explicitly justify absence of) required schema fields such as pressure, cycle counts, dosing/purge times, uniformity, conformality, roughness, density, and composition values from the article.
